        <abstract> 
<p>Asks to borrow W. C. Hewitson’s book [<hi rend="italic">British oology</hi>, 2 vols. (1831–44)].</p> 
            <p>CD is searching for reliable information on slight variations in the degree of perfection of nests of the same species of birds.</p>
